{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "payport-event-engine-collection",
		"name": "Payport Event Engine",
		"description": "API collection for Payport Event Engine (Codename: LIVEWIRE) - Real-time payment event streaming for frontend take-home assignments.\n\n## Overview\n- Time-bound 8-hour assignment system\n- SSE-based real-time payment event streaming\n- Multiple traffic simulation modes\n- Pre-approved candidate whitelist\n\n## Admin Flow (Before Candidate)\n1. Add candidate email to eligible list via `/admin/candidates`\n2. Share assignment link with candidate\n\n## Candidate Flow\n1. Start assignment with `/start` (must be pre-approved)\n2. Connect to `/events` for real-time payment stream\n3. Test with `/test/mode` to switch traffic modes\n4. Check time with `/time-remaining`\n5. Submit with `/stop`",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
