							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/start",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["start"]
						},
						"description": "Start the 8-hour assignment timer for a candidate.\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `name`: Candidate's full name\n- `email`: Valid email format (must be pre-approved by admin)\n- `github`: GitHub profile URL (format: https://github.com/username)\n\n**Validation:**\n- Email must be in the eligible candidates list (added by admin)\n- Email must be valid format\n- GitHub URL must be valid profile URL\n- Each email can only be used once\n\n**Response:**\n- `message`: Confirmation\n- `endsAt`: ISO timestamp when assignment expires"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Success",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
