		{
			"name": "Events (SSE)",
			"description": "Server-Sent Events endpoint for real-time payment streaming",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Payment Events Stream",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "text/event-stream"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/events?email={{email}}",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["events"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "email",
									"value": "{{email}}"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Connect to real-time payment event stream (SSE).\n\n**Requires:** Active session (call `/start` first)\n\n**Query params:**\n- `email`: Candidate's email\n\n**Event types:**\n- `connected`: Initial connection confirmation\n- `mode_changed`: Traffic mode was changed\n- `session_ended`: Assignment time expired\n- Payment events with: `eventId`, `timestamp`, `amount`, `currency`, `country`, `paymentMethod`, `source`, `status`\n\n**Payment Methods:** CARD, APPLE_PAY, GOOGLE_PAY, KLARNA, AFTERPAY, PAYPAL, CARD_INSTALLMENT\n\n**Countries:** US (USD), GB (GBP), Canada (CAD), Australia (AUD), UAE (AED), Germany (EUR), India (INR)\n\n**Sources:** web, mobile, api\n\n**Status:** success (95%), failed (5%)\n\n**Note:** Use browser EventSource or curl to test SSE. Postman shows raw stream."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Payment Event Example",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"body": "data: {\"type\":\"connected\",\"mode\":\"normal\"}\n\ndata: {\"eventId\":\"evt_abc123\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-13T10:30:00.000Z\",\"amount\":249.99,\"currency\":\"USD\",\"country\":\"US\",\"paymentMethod\":\"CARD\",\"source\":\"web\",\"status\":\"success\"}\n\ndata: {\"eventId\":\"evt_def456\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-13T10:30:01.000Z\",\"amount\":89.50,\"currency\":\"EUR\",\"country\":\"Germany\",\"paymentMethod\":\"KLARNA\",\"source\":\"mobile\",\"status\":\"success\"}\n\ndata: {\"eventId\":\"evt_ghi789\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-13T10:30:02.000Z\",\"amount\":150.00,\"currency\":\"CAD\",\"country\":\"Canada\",\"paymentMethod\":\"APPLE_PAY\",\"source\":\"mobile\",\"status\":\"success\"}"
						},
						{
							"name": "No Active Session",
							"status": "Forbidden",
							"code": 403,
							"body": "{\n    \"error\": \"No active session. Start assignment first.\"\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
